'''''Star Wars Insider'' 97''' is the ninety-seventh issue of the ''[[Star Wars Insider]]'' magazine and the fifth issue to be published by [[Titan Magazines]]. It was released to [[Wikipedia:United States|US]] newsstands on [[October 23]], [[2007]], and [[Wikipedia:United Kingdom|UK]] newsagents on [[October 25]], 2007.

{{Magazine-stub|issue}}

